title: The ✨BEST✨ No WiFi Game EVER!!!!
text:
I have been searching and searching and searching for a no WiFi game that is extremely fun. Subway surfers is INCREDIBLE!!!!!! There is always a few competitions to take part in, things you can get/achieve and very few ads!!! I let my sister play this game on my phone when she is bored, and she loves it. It has ads, but only after every 10 rounds or so. You don’t need WiFi or any service at all.
Basically what I’m trying to say is download it and you will not regret it!!

title: They actually made this game good!
text:
I started playing in 2018. Everything was alright, there were new countries, it was smooth.

But, in 2020, everything changed. We stopped having new countries, which was the sole reason why I downloaded this game in the first place.

But, all of a sudden, after 5 whole years, we actually got a new country: Ireland! Out of the entire time I’ve played this game, this is, by far, the best update I have EVER played.

The characters, the boards, the outfits (yes, plural). It was PERFECT.

So now I ask that you continue with this amazing cycle. Two new countries in a row? That would be awesome - maybe you could do Turkey (Istanbul) for Ramadan next!
